        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7a8444be-bdd7-4f48-a7ce-fb0e9651a810">
                Mr. Logan  (Liverpool, Scotland Division)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7a8444be-bdd7-4f48-a7ce-fb0e9651a810" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-07/debates/4ec9a334-46f3-407c-a59c-b8bb0978348f/CostOfLiving#contribution-7a8444be-bdd7-4f48-a7ce-fb0e9651a810">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it in order for an hon. Member to keep reading his speech?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7a8444be-bdd7-4f48-a7ce-fb0e9651a810" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-07/debates/4ec9a334-46f3-407c-a59c-b8bb0978348f/CostOfLiving#contribution-7a8444be-bdd7-4f48-a7ce-fb0e9651a810">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-9ef0814e-5145-449c-ac8d-a55d2ffd5beb">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9ef0814e-5145-449c-ac8d-a55d2ffd5beb">
