                Mr. Maudling
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0ea9180f-64c3-433b-af56-d5ebccd28bf1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
